    <title>Fissile materials</title>
    <chapter>
      <title>The stocks</title>
      <paragraph>The global inventory of highly enriched uranium (HEU) is estimated to be about 1370 ± 125 tonnes as of the end of 2014.</paragraph>
      <paragraph>The global stockpile of separated plutonium as of the end of 2014 is estimated as 506 ± 10 tonnes, of which about 272 tonnes is the material in civilian custod.</paragraph>

